    <title>odata url accessibility</title>
    <updated>2024-04-12T19:59:12.964000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>HemantVaswani</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/147458</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;Inside the SAP S4 HANA 2021 fully activated appliance, i have enabled the SAP gateway to access odata service.&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;I am able to successfully execute the&amp;nbsp; http and https using&amp;nbsp; the SAP Gateway Client in GUI&amp;nbsp; t code /n/IWFND/MAINT_SERVICES&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;same URLs are accessible in the browser&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;A href="http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/&lt;/A&gt; MD_SUPPLIER_MASTER_SRV&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;A href="http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/&lt;/A&gt; API_BUSINESS_PARTNER&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;A href="http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/&lt;/A&gt; API_SUPPLIERINVOICE_PROCESS&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;Although the following odata is getting successfully executed using&amp;nbsp; the SAP Gateway Client in GUI t code /n/IWFND/MAINT_SERVICES&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;FAP_VENDOR_LINE_ITEMS&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;While accessing through the browser, on prompt&amp;nbsp; of user id password, the above SAP GUI user id if provided, it's not allowing me to access&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;A href="http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/&lt;/A&gt; FAP_VENDOR_LINE_ITEMS&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;Please suggest some solution&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;The authorizations are checked and found to be in place, I mean the required ones are available&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;The url &lt;A href="http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;http://localhostfqdn/sap/opu/odata/sap/&lt;/A&gt; FAP_VENDOR_LINE_ITEMS&amp;nbsp; used with an entity set and a filter, its able to produce the data in the browser&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/odata-url-accessibility/qaq-p/13668567"/>
    <published>2024-04-12T19:59:12.964000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
